# ── Local diagnostic / simulation harnesses (NEVER commit) ─────
# Throwaway, isolated-SQLite diagnostic scripts and their regenerable
# artifacts. Kept out of the repo so the auto-commit session updater can
# never pollute this finance-system repo with temp tooling or sim captures.
_diag_*
_sim_ab_*
*.sqlite3
